internal partial class LimitedContext : JsonSerializerContext;
```

**Key takeaways (.NET 11 APIs):**

| API | Returns | Throws if missing? |
|-----|---------|-------------------|
| `options.GetTypeInfo<T>()` | `JsonTypeInfo<T>` | Yes |
| `options.TryGetTypeInfo<T>(out …)` | `bool` + nullable `JsonTypeInfo<T>` | No |

Use `GetTypeInfo<T>()` when you know the type is resolvable; use `TryGetTypeInfo<T>()` to safely branch without try/catch.
